{"id":"entities/beijing","title":"Beijing","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Beijing</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Capital city of <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/china\">China</a>. Yahir visited Nov 14-17, 2024 during his <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/shanghai-study-abroad\">CIEE Shanghai semester</a> — first documented Beijing trip in vault. First mentioned in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg\">2024 11 26 beijinggg</a> (4-day itinerary covering <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/forbidden-city\">Forbidden City</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/tiananmen-square\">Tiananmen Square</a>, Mutianyu <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/great-wall\">Great Wall</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/summer-palace\">Summer Palace</a>, Sanlitun, Wangfujing).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/china\">china</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/shanghai\">shanghai</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">china chapter</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/forbidden-city\">forbidden city</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/tiananmen-square\">tiananmen square</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/great-wall\">great wall</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/summer-palace\">summer palace</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg\">2024 11 26 beijinggg</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2024-11-26-beijinggg","label":"BEIJINGGG — Beijing 4-day itinerary (Nov 2024)"},{"id":"entities/china","label":"China"},{"id":"concepts/china-chapter","label":"China Chapter"},{"id":"entities/forbidden-city","label":"Forbidden